  ## What is iBridge  

  iBridge is a ministry by Graduates Christian Fellowship of Malaysia (GCF) that is focused on young graduates. It is mainly made up of young Malaysia Christian graduates who aims to Follow Jesus in every aspect of their life.

  ## Our Mission

  iBridge aims to encourage networking, spiritual friendship and mentoring among young Christian graduates in Malaysia.

  * Networking to connect lives in transition
  * Spiritual Friendships to cultivate praying partners.
  * Mentoring to create lifelong disciples.

  ## Our Activities

  If you are a young Christian graduate struggling to:

  * transition from campus to the marketplace,
  * follow God in the "real world",
  * find meaning in your work,
  * keep your faith alive...

